# Workflow

Follow [`docs/RULES.md`](docs/RULES.md) items **23** and **24**:

- Before changing behavior or structure, read relevant files under `docs/` (at minimum `docs/RULES.md`; also `docs/ARCHITECTURE.md` / `docs/TASKS.md` when applicable).
- After any code change, run the full test suite and fix failures before stopping: `npm run test` and `cargo test --manifest-path server/Cargo.toml`.
